name: Matabolong's Avocado Journal 002
description: The bus was surprisingly clean and neat. I sat at the back row to enjoy the scenery on the left side. There's no glass on the window. As I was enjoying the view, strange things come into my sight, things that shouldn't have been there in the first place. After passing a long tunnel, the mountain range starts to show, and a strong gust of wind blows through the open window.
